== 製作 ==
2020年7月，皮克斯宣佈正在製作一部名為《Luca》的電影。該片由{{le|恩里科·卡薩羅薩|Enrico Casarosa}}執導，{{le|麥克·瓊斯 (編劇)|Mike Jones (screenwriter)|麥克·瓊斯}}和{{le|傑西·安德魯斯|Jesse Andrews}}編劇，而{{le|安德麗亞·華倫|Anderia Walon}}擔任製片人<ref name="PixarLucaDeadline" />。卡薩羅薩表示該片靈感來自他在[[熱那亞|熱那亞]]的童年，並結合了[[費德里柯·費里尼|費德里柯·費里尼]]和[[宮崎駿|宮崎駿]]的元素<ref name="LucaEmpire1">{{cite web |last1=Travis |first1=Ben |date=2021-01-18 |title=Luca: The Inspiration Behind Pixar's Mythical Coming-Of-Age Adventure - Exclusive Image |url=https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/luca-pixar-mythical-coming-of-age-exclusive-image/ |work=[[Empire|Empire]] |access-date=2021-02-11 |archive-date=2021-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210210014604/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/luca-pixar-mythical-coming-of-age-exclusive-image/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年2月，宣佈[[雅各·特倫布雷|雅各·特倫布雷]]、[[傑克·狄倫·葛雷瑟|傑克·狄倫·葛雷瑟]]、艾瑪·伯曼、[[瑪雅·魯道夫|瑪雅·魯道夫]]、馬可·巴里切利和{{le|吉姆·加菲根|Jim Gaffigan}}加盟配音陣容<ref name="VarietyCast">{{cite web |last=Evans |first=Greg |title=‘Luca’ Teaser: Disney And Pixar Announce Voice Cast, Unveil Trailer For Upcoming Animated Feature |url=https://deadline.com/2021/02/luca-teaser-trailer-disney-pixar-voice-cast-jacob-tremblay-jim-gaffigan-1234700866/ |work=[[Variety|Variety]] |date=2021-02-25 |access-date=2021-02-25}}</ref>。

